summary: ...OCTAVE MOVING WEST-NORTHWESTWARD AND HOLDING STEADY... As of 8:00 PM PDT Fri Oct 03 the center of Octave was located near 13.8, -122.7 with movement WNW at 8 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1000 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 60 mph.
